  "detailed_description": "<strong>HANZ Puppetguns</strong> - is a multiplayer top-down shooter that will make you feel like a real toy hero! At your disposal will be one of four plush rabbits, a variety of weapons and an absolute random and fun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894830/extras/d154875298ccc949d9d7cec8ba45d435.poster.avif?t=1534388421\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894830/extras/d154875298ccc949d9d7cec8ba45d435.webm?t=1534388421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894830/extras/d154875298ccc949d9d7cec8ba45d435.mp4?t=1534388421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will have only one task - to survive. Survive in a fight with zombie wolves, who will try to bite off a piece from you, as well as with other players who also want your loot. The game generates absolutely random events, so the gaming experience will be constantly changing. Your actions will depend, for example, on whether you have found a steep machine gun or still trying to beat off enemies with the help of a shovel. The strongest survives!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Absolute randomness of everything!<br></li><li> A huge variety of weapons!<br></li><li> Character customization!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>HANZ Puppetguns</strong> - is a multiplayer top-down shooter that will make you feel like a real toy hero! At your disposal will be one of four plush rabbits, a variety of weapons and an absolute random and fun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894830/extras/d154875298ccc949d9d7cec8ba45d435.poster.avif?t=1534388421\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894830/extras/d154875298ccc949d9d7cec8ba45d435.webm?t=1534388421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/894830/extras/d154875298ccc949d9d7cec8ba45d435.mp4?t=1534388421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will have only one task - to survive. Survive in a fight with zombie wolves, who will try to bite off a piece from you, as well as with other players who also want your loot. The game generates absolutely random events, so the gaming experience will be constantly changing. Your actions will depend, for example, on whether you have found a steep machine gun or still trying to beat off enemies with the help of a shovel. The strongest survives!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Absolute randomness of everything!<br></li><li> A huge variety of weapons!<br></li><li> Character customization!</li></ul>",
